715631f-a.title: Manhattan: 141st Street (West) - Edgecombe Avenue
715631f-a.text:
311-323 West 141st Street, east of,adjoining, and at the
S.E. corner of Edgecombe Avenue. Nos. 313-315 are three-story
frame houses with plaster fronts.
1932.
J. Clarencc Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 384.
CREDIT LINE IPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.

719622f-a.title: Manhattan: Edgecombe Avenue - 141st Street
719622f-a.text:
204-188 Edgecombe Avenue, east side, between 145th and 141st Streets
(142nd and 143rd Streets do not intersect Edgecombe Avenue). The
two small houses in the centre, 200-198 Edgecombe Avenue,are frame
structures, the latter with a stucco front.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 403.
CREUIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALD REPRODUCTIONS.
